MID_支援_アサマ_カザハナ_Ａ: $t1$Wmカザハナ|7$w0|$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E怒,|Well now, today for the sake of my\nsword practice, I'll cut this tree down!$k\n$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|Don't do it, Kazahana!!$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E通常,|Ah. Asama... What's up?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E苦,|"What's up", is not it!$k$pWhy did you arrive ahead of me,\nwhen you didn't even call?$k$pThe time when you go and train is\nwhen we go together, or was that$k$pnot our agreement?$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Ahh... I must've forgotten.\nSorry～! Heehee!$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|Don't you "heehee" me!$k$pDespite our agreement, you've already\nwent out for training alone for a third time?$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E苦,|Gah. S-so what if I did?!$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,汗|The first time, you sliced the tree from its\nbase, so that when it collided with the earth$k$pI could feel the vibrations through my feet.\nI was close to nearly falling in the mud.$k$pThe second time, you let out a yell of\nsurprise, so I was attacked by a flock$k$pof escaping bats. The third time,\nyou had rushed on ahead with your$k$pkatana, already drawing it from its sheath...\nThe pit of my stomach jumped.$k$pYes, that's it.\nThis is the thing you lost!!$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E通常,汗|A-ahaha... Thanks... After that I tried\nlooking for it, but couldn't find it...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|That's good, then!$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E苦,|But, what do you mean third time?\nDid I not call out for you...?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E苦,|Seems that three times wasn't enough\nto get the impact of my words across.$k$pReally...what the heck is this...?\nPerhaps this is some sort of punishment...?$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E通常,|Hm, maybe so.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|"Maybe so", my foot...\nAt any rate, today we shall travel together.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$WaYep, gotcha.$k\n$Wc$Sbv40|1000|$Fo1000|$Sbv100|1000|$Fi1000|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E苦,|As expected... Going along with you to not\nmeet with any injury was part of my reading.$k$pToday, with no signs of injuries...\nIt's a miracle.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E笑,|Ahahaha, is that so?\nStranger things could've happened.$k$pSurely, up until