MID_支援_アサマ_カザハナ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmカザハナ|7$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E怒,照|Asama... Are you fine now?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|What is it, Kazahana? Are you possibly\ngoing to train with your sword again?$k$pIn that case, I'd have to tag along.$k$pI was just wondering exactly\nwhen I'd climb the mountain.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$WaUmm... It's a little different.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaWhat is it? Do you believe that it is\nannoying when I accompany you?$k$pHaven't I said before why we\ngo together? It is for my sake...!$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Th-that's not it!$k$pI'm saying that...you and I should\nbe together forever from now on...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E苦,|So? It's only natural to\nrequest this sort of...$k$p$E苦,照|...Huh?$k$pF-forever...?!$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$WaY-yeah... Not only when we go to\nthe mountain to do our practices,$k$pI mean, together forever\nis what I mean...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,照|Is that a confession of love...?\nBut, why me...?$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E怒,照|In the many times I was able\nto practice in the mountains...$k$pI had felt anxiously lonely\non various occasions...$k$pThe times when you were nearby,\nit was fun and reassuring.$k$pThat's why I thought about you\nand I being together, forever...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaSo, that was it...\nThat surprised me a little...$k$p$Eキメ,照|...There is no reason\nfor me to refuse.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Huh...?!$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaPerhaps until now...$k$pIt was no accident that we'd encountered\none another in the middle of the mountains.$k$pI suppose this is some sort of revelation...\nthat I would always be beside you...$k$pIt was fate that you would\nbe my companion.$k$p...Or, so the gods would say.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E笑,照|Th-then...?!$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,照|Correct. Not only when we go\nto the mountain to practice,$k$pwe'll be together, always.$k$pWe should bestow this\nrelationship of ours.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$WaY-yeah...! Thank you,\nAsama. I love you.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaRight, as do I.$k
